Text: I am so embarrassed for her. What a cheesy Paris Hilton knock off. The sex scene is so sad and desperate looking. She would, at this point, sell her left tit to get her career back. However, this pathetic cry for attention will not do it for her. The most pathetic video I have ever seen. Desperate... that's all I can say.... so very desperate... and sad.
You are so right. I wanted to see her sweet ass for about 20 years, and aside from a few select minutes, this is like watching a train wreck. Sad, very sad.
